sources.title: Rainbow Ranch (1933) REX BELL
sources.description:
Stars: Rex Bell, Cecilia Parker, Bob Kortman
Director: Harry L. Fraser

An emergency at his aunt's ranch gets Ed Randall leave from the Navy. He returns to find the water cut off and her note due the next day.

metadata.Plot: An emergency at his Aunt's ranch gets Ed Randall leave from the Navy. He returns to find the water cut off and her note due the next day. When the man he seeks legal advice from is murdered, Ed is accused and he now finds himself in jail with a lynch mob forming outside.
metadata.Actors: Rex Bell, Cecilia Parker, Bob Kortman
